Rebuild book / generate / about per kineticcare_claude_code_prompt.md

book.html — 3-step wizard:
- Step 1: name, email, phone (+91 prefix, 10-digit validation)
- Step 2: concern (6 icon cards) + consultation mode (2 large toggles)
- Step 3: time preference pills + optional notes (300 char counter)
- Progress dots + step label, slide animation between steps
- Right-column sticky trust panel: SVG clinic illustration, live
  pill, 3 trust rows (response/address/hours), patient quote,
  trust badges
- Formspree hook (FORM_ID placeholder — paste real endpoint later)
- localStorage fallback if Formspree unreachable
- Success state with reference ID + booking summary + CTAs
- beforeunload guard, double-submit protection, aria-busy, aria-live
- URL param pre-fill: ?plan=essential|pro|corporate, ?concern=X
- Mobile: single column, trust panel collapses, time pills wrap

generate.html — 2D canvas rewrite (no Three.js):
- drawSpine(ctx, W, H) with 24 procedural vertebrae (7C + 12T + 5L)
- Forward lean from desk hours, lumbar lordosis flattening with age,
  disk compression from age, pelvis scale by gender, pelvic width
- Ribcage ellipses, pulse rings on strained regions
- Light-mode opacity multiplier (om = 2.5) + warm radial tint
- View toggles: Front / 3/4 / Side (rotation offset)
- Drag to rotate, scroll to zoom, arrow-key orbit when focused
- Recenter button (click and Space / Enter when focused)
- Debounced regeneration (200ms), pulse animation on input change
- Risk badge (Low / Moderate / High) based on desk + age
- Clinical interpretation list with specific numbers + weeks
- Recommended service card → services.html#{anchor}
- CTA → book.html?concern=X
- Canvas-context fallback (no DevTools text) if 2D unavailable
- DPR-aware, IntersectionObserver + visibilitychange pause

about.html — editorial layout:
- Hero: "Our Story · Indiranagar, 2019" eyebrow + 84px display H1
  with accent "answered the question" + 3 hero pills
- 2-column story + vertical timeline (5 nodes, 2026 marked current
  with pulse ring)
- Principles: 3 full-width alternating-bg cards with 72px Syne
  numbered step + principle name H3 + body
- Team: 3-card row with initials avatars (gradient) + role + bio
- Stats band: 4 counters (12,000K+ / 3x / 94% / 6yr) — uses
  shared.js IntersectionObserver counter
- Final CTA: quoted section header + book CTA
- BreadcrumbList schema (Home → About)
- Fully responsive, prefers-reduced-motion aware

services.html — already matches the prompt structure; no changes
needed beyond shared.css/js wiring done in prior commit.

